4 December 2008Government Spokesperson, Mr Themba Maseko, will address a media briefing on South Africa s response to the food crisis in Zimbabwe.The Director-General of Public Enterprises, Portia Molefe, will join the briefing.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: 5 December 2008 Time: 10:00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNote: There will be a video link to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Enquiries Harold Maloka Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)